        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Build a Better VA Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits funds from being appropriated for any fiscal year for a Department of Veterans Affairs major medical facility lease unless the House and Senate Committees on Veterans' Affairs adopt resolutions approving the lease. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
